
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-ietf-stir-certificates-ocsp-00.txt'>
    <title>"OCSP Usage for Secure Telephone Identity Certificates", Jon Peterson, Sean Turner</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-ietf-stir-certificates-ocsp-00.txt</link>
    <description>When certificates are used as credentials to attest the assignment or ownership of telephone numbers, some mechanism is required to convey certificate freshness to relying parties.  This document specifies the use of the Online Certificate Status Protocol (OCSP) as a means of retrieving real-time status information about such certificates, defining new extensions to compensate for the dynamism of telephone number assignments.</description>
    <dc:date>2017-03-13T07:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
